# **ğŸ“Š Attendance Management System **

## **ğŸš€ Project Overview**
A comprehensive, role-based **Employee Attendance & Leave Management System** built with modern Java technologies. This system streamlines employee attendance tracking, leave management, shift scheduling, and regularization processes for organizations of all sizes.

![Java](https://img.shields.io/badge/Java-ED8B00?style=for-the-badge&logo=openjdk&logoColor=white)
![Spring Boot](https://img.shields.io/badge/Spring_Boot-6DB33F?style=for-the-badge&logo=spring-boot&logoColor=white)
![MySQL](https://img.shields.io/badge/MySQL-4479A1?style=for-the-badge&logo=mysql&logoColor=white)
![Thymeleaf](https://img.shields.io/badge/Thymeleaf-005F0F?style=for-the-badge&logo=thymeleaf&logoColor=white)

## **âœ¨ Key Features**

### **ğŸ‘¥ Multi-Role Authentication**
- **ğŸ‘‘ Admin Panel**: Full system control, user management, reports
- **ğŸ‘¨â€ğŸ’¼ Manager Dashboard**: Team oversight, leave approvals
- **ğŸ‘· Employee Portal**: Attendance marking, leave applications, self-service

### **ğŸ“… Core Modules**
| Module | Features | Access Level |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| **Attendance Tracking** | Clock-in/out, location tracking, monthly reports | All Users |
| **Leave Management** | Apply/approve leaves, multiple leave types | All Users |
| **Shift Management** | Define shifts, swap requests | All Users |
| **Regularization** | Attendance correction requests | All Users |
| **Holiday Calendar** | Company holidays, recurring events | All Users |
| **Reports & Analytics** | Attendance reports, leave statistics | Admin/Manager |

## **ğŸ› ï¸ Technology Stack**

### **Backend**
- **Java 17** - Core programming language
- **Spring Boot 3.1.5** - Rapid application development
- **Spring Security** - Authentication & authorization
- **Spring Data JPA** - Database operations
- **Spring MVC** - Web framework
- **Hibernate** - ORM framework

### **Frontend**
- **Thymeleaf** - Server-side templating
- **HTML5** - Markup
- **CSS3** - Styling
- **JavaScript** - Client-side interactions
- **Bootstrap** - Responsive design (optional)

### **Database**
- **MySQL 8.0** - Relational database
- **H2 Database** - Testing/Development (optional)

### **Tools & Libraries**
- **Maven** - Dependency management
- **Lombok** - Code reduction
- **JUnit 5** - Unit testing
- **Spring Boot DevTools** - Hot reload

